      "raw_text": "(1) AT 12APR26 0000Z, TYPHOON 04W (SINLAKU) WAS LOCATED \nNEAR 9.9N 151.2E, APPROXIMATELY 440 NM EAST-SOUTHEAST OF NAVSTA \nGUAM, AND HAD TRACKED NORTH-NORTHWESTWARD AT 08 KNOTS OVER THE \nPAST SIX HOURS. MAXIMUM SUSTAINED SURFACE WINDS WERE ESTIMATED \nAT 110 KNOTS GUSTING TO 135 KNOTS. SEE REF A (WTPN31 PGTW 120300) \nFOR FURTHER DETAILS.",
